      <title>日本央行行长发表谨慎言论 日元押注承压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/stronger-yen-pressure-on-stocks-among-top-calls-after-boj-holds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们原本希望日本央行行长上田一夫在周五的新闻发布会上发表强硬言论，但结果却令他们感到失望，日元上涨的希望也破灭了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/stronger-yen-pressure-on-stocks-among-top-calls-after-boj-holds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 04:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
